flowchart LR
    Client([Client])
    API[Search API]
    GeoIndex[Geo Index Lookup<br/>Geohash / Quadtree]
    GeoCache[(In-Memory<br/>Geo Cache)]
    BizDB[(Business Store<br/>transactional)]
    Filter[Hydrate +<br/>Haversine Filter]
    ResultCache[(Result Cache<br/>hot queries)]

    Client -->|lat,lng,radius| API
    API -->|cached page| ResultCache
    ResultCache -.->|miss| GeoIndex
    GeoIndex -->|cell + neighbors| GeoCache
    GeoCache -->|candidate ids| Filter
    Filter -->|hydrate| BizDB
    Filter -->|sorted results| API
    API --> Client

